		/obj/item/food/boiledegg,
		/obj/item/surprise_egg
	))

/datum/storage/basket/easter/handle_enter(datum/source, obj/item/arrived)
	. = ..()
	countEggs(source)

/datum/storage/basket/easter/proc/countEggs(obj/item/storage/basket/easter/basket)
